sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User
  participant APP as Flutter App
  participant EDGE as ALB or API Gateway
  participant RECO as Recommendation Service
  participant RDS as RDS

  U->>APP: Swipe card
  APP->>EDGE: POST swipe action
  EDGE->>RECO: Record swipe

  RECO->>RDS: Insert swipe history
  RDS-->>RECO: OK

  alt Swipe right
    RECO->>RDS: Save like record
    RDS-->>RECO: OK
  end

  RECO-->>EDGE: Success
  EDGE-->>APP: Success
  APP-->>U: Show next card
